_config.scss.description:
**SCSS config文件**<br>
**注意：项目使用前必须通过webpack配置config地址**<br>
**使用方法：**<br>
```
【webpack配置方法】
//须在wepack文件中配置类似地址配置，或使用此处默认值
const cf= path.resolve(__dirname, "./node_modules/@netease/urs-rui/src/scss");
const sassLoader =   ExtractTextPlugin.extract("style", "css!sass-loader?sourceMap=true&includePaths[]="+cf);

//或者
const cf= path.resolve(__dirname, "./node_modules/@netease/urs-rui/src/scss");
module: {
    rules: [{
        test: /\.scss$/,
        use: [{
            loader: "style-loader"
        }, {
            loader: "css-loader"
        }, {
            loader: "sass-loader",
            options: {
                includePaths: [cf]
            }
        }]
    }]
}
```
